title: The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', but it changes with settings.
description: The bug report is incomplete and does not provide enough context to understand the issue. Please provide more information about the settings that are causing the title of the hyperlink builder to change.
OB: Clicking on 'OK' and reopening the hyperlink builder results in the title changing to 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The expected behavior is that the title of the hyperlink builder should always be 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'. 2. Click 'OK'. 3. Reopen the hyperlink builder and observe the title.
